messages.speech:
Transitions in careers can be seamless or rocky and most often comes untold and involuntary. Handling the voluntary and involuntary can get stressful. Having a conversation with higher ups for voluntary transitions and resetting to the new normal is essential. The handling of the transition involves How to identify the symptoms , and When to initiate these conversations and What are the signals that one sees when these transitions are about to happen.
How else can I help you ?
